Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:02:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:20.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:29.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:40.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:44.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:49.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:55.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:01:02.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:07.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:26.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:30.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:35.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:42.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:48.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:53.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:55.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:02:00.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:15.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:19.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:33.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:39.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a quiet night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on watch, but it's \Nbeen calm all night long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need to man the helm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working myself to the bone for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that I'm all bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Luffy-san and his buddies?\NI've joined their crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are great people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they are more than just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found something incredible\Nearlier this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It told of Luffy-san and his crew's fearsome\Nadventures and their battle-filled days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I have joined them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must prove that I am worthy\Nto call myself a crewmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you agree, Laboon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wake you up with a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ White handkerchief, ♪\N--Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ don't let him find you ♪\N--The sun hasn't risen yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ Run for it ♪\N--Let me catch some more Z's!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ White handkerchief... ♪\N--Forget Brook. Someone make\NLuffy stop snoring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Brook's Great Struggle! Is the Path\Nto Becoming a True Comrade Rigorous?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the plan, Navigator?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we use the paddle, we could keep\Nmoving through these calm waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on the weather,\Nthis lull should only last today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we don't need to use our precious cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good!\NSanji, your cooking really is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan, have a second\Nhelping of the seafood salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you been so hyper all morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something exciting happen, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he saw our ship's log\Nwhile he was on watch yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I just so happened\Nto read a small portion of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, it left me astonished!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to \Nsettle down ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incident at Thriller Bark was\Nonly the tip of the iceberg for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stopped a civil war in\Nthe desert kingdom, Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a grand adventure\Non the legendary sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, you took on \Nthe World Government in a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,massive fight at Water Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so surprised, I \Nnearly had a heart attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I don't have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I wonder what sort of stories\Nwill get added to the log.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook, your name is going to\Nstart appearing in it now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that! Now that I am your crewmate,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is imperative that I make myself useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get why you're eager to work hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbut first let me give you a word of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to hear it, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this crew, never let your\Nguard down during a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! I, Quick Draw Brook, shall be
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nready for the enemy to strike at any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently we didn't warn you soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I claim those noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.19,0:06:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please wait a second! Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should not have let my guard down,\Neven for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well! I shall work \Nmyself to the bone to become
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a true pal as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm already nothing but bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it. Since \Nyou're washing the dishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can take my time with Nami-san's tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As your pal, I am dying to help\Neveryone in extravagant ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll do anything to make\Nmyself useful for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a great attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm a skeleton, I should work\Ntill I'm bone tired on the small stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going to give Nami-san her tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Sanji-san, where do these go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, over in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drop them, even if it kills you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--And "kaboom!"\N--Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust you to do the dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then I'll take this \Ntea to Nami-san instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait! I was gonna take it to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, I've brought you some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I see your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bam!\N--That came out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a nautical chart?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been pretty busy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a great chance to work on it,\Nsince the ship isn't going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it your dream to \Ndraw a map of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I want to navigate\Nacross the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make a world map based on what I've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is anything\NI could do to help, please let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, would you like another cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sentiment is enough for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are both beautiful and humble!\NNami-san, you truly are wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really! I'm not that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you truly are--ouch! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, I nearly burned my fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I have any skin to burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My map!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have I done?!\NThat was horribly careless of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! I wiped it clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you wiped it clean of everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking my leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling that I won't be\Nthe least bit useful if this keeps up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two are about to do something neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper-san, what are you doing up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm drying these herbs in the sun,\Nsince the weather is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, Franky is gonna test his new weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! This is the long-distance\N"Super Franky Cannon."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It runs on cola energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its range is several times
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that of a conventional cannon. \NPlus it's super accurate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Combined with my sniper skills,\Nwe'll be totally unstoppable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have butterflies in my stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Let me know if there\Nis anything I could do to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. In that case, please get\Nanother barrel of cola to play it safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a problem. It would be my pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the barrel of cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Now if you could pour it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target: That rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Locking on to the rock at 2 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Fire!\N--Firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, increase the pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a huge flop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should have worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is kinda salty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is mixed with the cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show a little remorse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mistook a soy sauce barrel\Nfor a cola barrel, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right! This \Nwas a soy sauce barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannon believe I made that mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm terribly sorry!\N--Why did you grab a soy sauce barrel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm sorry!\N--This is no time for puns!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook, you're hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't give me any "I'm only bones" crap!\N--Now I'm all sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I have to wash all of\Nthe herbs I had set out to dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This meat tastes great\Nwith the soy sauce and cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.86,0:12:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you find a bright side to anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I try ends up going horribly awry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Zoro-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to watch in admiration!\NI'm a fellow swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this meditation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You enter a state of nothingness\Nwhile making your mind and body one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Zoro-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am fully aware that it is improper to\Ntalk during meditation sessions, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well, you see...\N--What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to use the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't need to know that! Head on over--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The thing is...\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my legs went numb, so I can't stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any muscles to go numb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro-san, I'm on the verge\Nof having an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real? W-Wait, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm gonna leak! It's coming!\N--I'll take you! W-Wait! Hey, hold it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite what I want, I've \Nbeen nothing but a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I could \Ndo to be of assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook, why are you so anxious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anxious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling you're afraid\Nof something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are absolutely right, Robin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I am terribly \Nanxious and scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Luffy-san first asked me\Nto join his crew, I was thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those simple words filled me with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then my heart danced
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with excitement when I defeated \NOars alongside everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I join your crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But does he truly want me in his crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we continue to head toward the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no doubt that powerful foes and\Ntrials beyond our imagination await us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:15:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that I will be\Nboth useless and a hindrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that proves true, I
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,might get kicked off the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I'm afraid\Nof losing my friends again
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and returning to that\Npainfully long life of solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...also anxious for the longest of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...also anxious for the longest of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was constantly afraid that I\Nwas unworthy to be their friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I believed I could\Nbecome worthy of them
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by throwing away my life for their sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far I go on the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a huge enemy that I can't shake off...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because the world and\Nits darkness are my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't want\Nyou to come to rescue me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm going to die someday anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die right here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize that was how you felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't what it means to be a true friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oomph!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook, we've got food! It's lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji worked extra hard to make\Na full-course seafood lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just know it'll be good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's keeping you? Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you absolutely certain I'm welcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NThat I may join the Straw Hat Crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, give it some thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to let you join,\Nso I'm glad to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now forget about that. Let's eat! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Straw Hats have \Ncalm days like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, let's catch dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years--no, decades--has it been
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nsince I enjoyed such a carefree nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook! Are you gonna sleep forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! We spotted an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a summer island! It has a beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was wandering the ocean alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would dream about my old\Nfriends and Laboon in my sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would jump awake with happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only to face the painful reality\Nfilled with despair and solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep was by no means a peaceful escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I listen carefully now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Robin, what do you \Nthink of these outfits?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think you'd look \Ngood in this and this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My pals are near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even dead and skeletonized...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm truly glad to be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.47,0:22:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a short break time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.57,0:22:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before the next adventure \Neventually falls upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let your weary bones rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.73,0:22:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it looks like I will have
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a slew of stories to \Nshare when we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're looking forward to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:22:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind has picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.32,0:23:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.29,0:23:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oomph!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time we set out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to work my butt off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.27,0:23:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a skeleton, so I don't have a butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've reached the Red Line at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll finally get to see Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.78,0:23:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the mermaids?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any mermaids,\Nbut there is a sea monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.02,0:23:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something popped out\Nwhen I whacked its stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.96,0:23:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.03,0:23:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be a--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.26,0:23:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Halfway Across the Grand Line!\NArrival at the Red Line!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.12,0:23:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
